624static const EmbReal emb_constant_pi = 3.14159265358979323846;
625
626/*
627 * \brief Convert \a a to a QPointF.
628 */
629inline QPointF
630to_QPointF(EmbVector a)
631{
632 QPointF result(a.x, a.y);
633 return result;
634}
635
636/*
637 * \brief Convert \a a to an EmbVector.
638 */
639inline EmbVector
640to_EmbVector(QPointF a)
641{
642 EmbVector v;
643 v.x = a.x();
644 v.y = a.y();
645 return v;
646}
647
648/*
649 * \brief Wrapper for embVector_add to use the syntax \a a + \a b.
650 */
651inline EmbVector
652operator+(EmbVector a, EmbVector b)
653{
654 return embVector_add(a, b);
655}
656
657/*
658 * \brief Wrapper for embVector_subtract to use the syntax \a a - \a b.
659 */
660inline EmbVector
661operator-(EmbVector a, EmbVector b)
662{
663 return embVector_subtract(a, b);
664}
665
669inline EmbReal
670radians(EmbReal degrees)
671{
672 return (degrees*emb_constant_pi/180.0);
673}
674
678inline EmbReal
679degrees(EmbReal radian)
680{
681 return (radian*180.0/emb_constant_pi);
682}
